{"Id":732334,"Title":"停云四章赠允初","Dynasty":"清","Author":"彭绩","Context":"霭霭停云，悠悠我思。袭我春服，好风时吹。我征聿至，乃入园扉。鸟鸣嘉木，鱼跃清池。其物欣欣，其人在斯。我息其庐，话言《诗》《书》。寒葵载刈，旨酒盈壶。以觞以咏，其乐于于。凄凄风雨，笥衣授余。乃空汝床，曰安我居。飘风及雨，诘旦乃已。我晨斯兴，于阁间止。阅彼南亩，实活我士。和泽之降，河水瀰瀰。息彼黄牛，我心之喜。庭列松篁，日翳轩窗。有鸟于飞，好音旁皇。薄言旋反，寻乐未央。嘉子栖迟，好学无荒。问我瑶华，心焉弗忘。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"cb5a621618df5db840f9ddff406d53c9","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5875420,"Sentence":"霭霭停云，悠悠我思。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"ǎi ǎi tǐng yún ，yōu yōu wǒ sāi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5875421,"Sentence":"袭我春服，好风时吹。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xǐ wǒ chūn fú ，hǎo fēng shǐ chuī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5875422,"Sentence":"我征聿至，乃入园扉。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ zhēng yù zhì ，nǎi rù yuán fēi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5875423,"Sentence":"鸟鸣嘉木，鱼跃清池。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"diǎo mǐng jiā mù ，yú yuè qīng chǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5875424,"Sentence":"其物欣欣，其人在斯。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jī wù xīn xīn ，jī rén zài sī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5875425,"Sentence":"我息其庐，话言《诗》《书》。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ xī jī lú ，huà yán 《shī 》《shū 》","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5875426,"Sentence":"寒葵载刈，旨酒盈壶。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hán kuǐ zǎi yì ，zhi jiu yīng hú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5875427,"Sentence":"以觞以咏，其乐于于。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yi shāng yi yǒng ，jī lè yú yú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5875428,"Sentence":"凄凄风雨，笥衣授余。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qī qī fēng yǔ ，sì yī shòu yú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"D